WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 6=

00:00:05.340 --> 00:00:06.700
Your Highness.

00:00:07.700 --> 00:00:10.140
Your Highness, Eunuch Xu has arrived.

00:00:10.680 --> 00:00:13.600
(Eunuch Xu, Eunuch to the Emperor
of Tianxuan Kingdom)

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:15.379
Here's the Emperor's verbal command.

00:00:15.380 --> 00:00:16.640
During tomorrow's morning court,

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:18.660
you're requested
to enter the palace for an audience.

00:00:19.860 --> 00:00:23.580
Your Highness, the Crown Prince fell ill
as soon as he returned to the palace.

00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:24.419
He...

00:00:24.420 --> 00:00:25.659
He filed a complaint against you,

00:00:25.660 --> 00:00:27.260
saying you allowed
a girl to commit violence

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:29.280
and attempted
to murder the Crown Prince.

00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:31.780
Please be careful
when you go to the palace tomorrow.

00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:39.960
(The Imperial Palace)

00:00:44.420 --> 00:00:45.339
Father,

00:00:45.340 --> 00:00:48.139
you must seek justice for me!

00:00:48.140 --> 00:00:49.420
Stand up and speak.

00:00:51.020 --> 00:00:53.740
I can't get up, Father.

00:00:54.100 --> 00:00:57.820
My whole body hurts so much, Father.

00:00:57.900 --> 00:00:59.099
It's all Prince Jing's fault.

00:00:59.100 --> 00:01:01.179
It's the little demon brat he picked up.

00:01:01.180 --> 00:01:03.220
She summoned wasps to sting me.

00:01:03.380 --> 00:01:06.219
She even colluded with Prince Jing
to swindle my money.

00:01:06.220 --> 00:01:07.459
She also...

00:01:07.460 --> 00:01:08.900
She...

00:01:08.980 --> 00:01:10.379
She's so eerie.

00:01:10.380 --> 00:01:13.820
You can tell she's no good, Father.

00:01:15.580 --> 00:01:17.800
Your Majesty, when the Crown Prince
returned to his manor,

00:01:17.800 --> 00:01:19.220
he was indeed barefoot

00:01:19.420 --> 00:01:20.499
with disheveled hair,

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:22.420
wearing nothing but his inner robes.

00:01:24.540 --> 00:01:26.139
Yes, Father.

00:01:26.140 --> 00:01:29.019
She bullied me so miserably.

00:01:29.020 --> 00:01:30.299
She also...

00:01:30.300 --> 00:01:31.540
She...

00:01:32.740 --> 00:01:34.539
What did you say she did before?

00:01:34.540 --> 00:01:35.980
I forgot my lines.

00:01:41.660 --> 00:01:44.660
She isn't human, Father.

00:01:45.740 --> 00:01:47.539
She's a demon brat descended
to the mortal world.

00:01:47.540 --> 00:01:48.539
♪Where she goes east♪

00:01:48.540 --> 00:01:49.379
♪The east has bad luck♪

00:01:49.380 --> 00:01:50.339
♪Where she goes west♪

00:01:50.340 --> 00:01:51.339
♪The west catches a plague♪

00:01:51.340 --> 00:01:52.259
♪She opens her mouth♪

00:01:52.260 --> 00:01:52.899
♪Disaster arrives♪

00:01:52.900 --> 00:01:54.059
♪She raises her hand♪

00:01:54.060 --> 00:01:54.819
♪Trouble finds you♪

00:01:54.820 --> 00:01:56.159
♪Wherever she stands♪

00:01:56.160 --> 00:01:58.859
♪Chickens fly and dogs jump in chaos♪

00:01:58.860 --> 00:02:00.500
Oh, Father, she...

00:02:01.820 --> 00:02:03.260
Out of lyrics.

00:02:03.300 --> 00:02:05.740
Who played that music?
They shall be rewarded.

00:02:23.220 --> 00:02:25.859
Crown Prince Uncle, you sang quite well.

00:02:25.860 --> 00:02:27.459
You're just a bit out of tune.

00:02:27.460 --> 00:02:29.259
Do you want me to teach you?

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:31.259
But I'll have to charge a fee.

00:02:31.260 --> 00:02:31.980
You.

00:02:34.020 --> 00:02:35.699
- Greetings, Father.
- Greetings, Grandfather.

00:02:35.700 --> 00:02:38.420
- Long live Your Majesty.
- Long live Your Majesty.

00:02:39.260 --> 00:02:40.540
You may rise.

00:02:42.460 --> 00:02:43.580
Is that Prince Jing?

00:02:43.700 --> 00:02:44.820
I must be seeing a ghost.

00:02:45.220 --> 00:02:46.699
Am I seeing things?

00:02:46.700 --> 00:02:49.099
In these past three years, this is
the first time I've seen him at court.

00:02:49.100 --> 00:02:49.779
Indeed.

00:02:49.780 --> 00:02:51.059
Look at his complexion.

00:02:51.060 --> 00:02:53.499
He doesn't look half-dead
like the Crown Prince said.

00:02:53.500 --> 00:02:56.179
He truly was the prince
the Emperor valued most.

00:02:56.180 --> 00:02:58.820
Even with broken legs,
he still looks radiant.

00:03:01.420 --> 00:03:02.780
Father, don't be afraid.

00:03:02.900 --> 00:03:04.020
I'm here.

00:03:06.020 --> 00:03:08.259
(Ever since Xiao Heng
was injured in the war,)

00:03:08.260 --> 00:03:09.419
(he has been depressed.)

00:03:09.420 --> 00:03:12.500
(He spent his days locked in his room
drinking and never came out.)

00:03:12.540 --> 00:03:14.339
(I thought he was already broken.)

00:03:14.340 --> 00:03:17.460
(I didn't expect him
to look like this at court today.)

00:03:19.100 --> 00:03:21.660
Prince Jing, you look well.

00:03:22.660 --> 00:03:24.100
It is thanks to your blessing, Father.

00:03:24.380 --> 00:03:27.499
I don't feel like
it's thanks to my blessing.

00:03:27.500 --> 00:03:30.580
I think it's more thanks
to this little girl's blessing.

00:03:32.460 --> 00:03:33.580
Yes.

00:03:33.940 --> 00:03:35.739
Ever since I adopted this child,

00:03:35.740 --> 00:03:38.579
my days have become different.

00:03:38.580 --> 00:03:39.899
You're welcome, Father.

00:03:39.900 --> 00:03:41.139
I like you very much.

00:03:41.140 --> 00:03:42.859
I also like Grandfather very much.

00:03:42.860 --> 00:03:44.859
You are people of great fortune

00:03:44.860 --> 00:03:47.300
and kind hearts.

00:03:47.700 --> 00:03:48.859
This little girl

00:03:48.860 --> 00:03:50.340
has a very sweet mouth.

00:03:51.460 --> 00:03:53.620
Hm, Father,

00:03:53.660 --> 00:03:55.179
don't listen to their pretenses.

00:03:55.180 --> 00:03:56.739
It's all an act.

00:03:56.740 --> 00:03:58.699
She coaxed me just like this yesterday

00:03:58.700 --> 00:04:01.019
and swindled all my things away.

00:04:01.020 --> 00:04:03.299
An adult who doesn't keep their word,

00:04:03.300 --> 00:04:05.579
asking back
for things given to others...

00:04:05.580 --> 00:04:07.179
Crown Prince Uncle, you're so stingy.

00:04:07.180 --> 00:04:08.620
You.

00:04:10.140 --> 00:04:13.019
Fine, let's just say
I was unlucky yesterday

00:04:13.020 --> 00:04:14.540
and fell into your trap.

00:04:14.660 --> 00:04:16.019
But Xiao Heng,

00:04:16.020 --> 00:04:18.459
taking in this wild girl
of unknown origin on your own

00:04:18.460 --> 00:04:20.179
is a disregard for the law

00:04:20.180 --> 00:04:21.939
and pollutes the imperial bloodline.

00:04:21.940 --> 00:04:25.500
What's more, this girl is a jinx.

00:04:25.860 --> 00:04:26.579
A jinx?

00:04:26.580 --> 00:04:28.100
They say she's a jinx?

00:04:29.420 --> 00:04:30.940
This is quite improper.

00:04:31.220 --> 00:04:33.779
Your Majesty,
I have a petition to present.

00:04:33.780 --> 00:04:34.919
I have heard

00:04:34.920 --> 00:04:38.460
that the Little Princess of
Prince Jing Manor is of unknown origin

00:04:38.500 --> 00:04:41.139
and was born ill-omened.

00:04:41.140 --> 00:04:42.899
My hometown is in Lin'an City,

00:04:42.900 --> 00:04:44.899
and I've heard
the rumors about this girl.

00:04:44.900 --> 00:04:45.779
Whatever she says

00:04:45.780 --> 00:04:47.459
comes true.

00:04:47.460 --> 00:04:49.420
It's eerie.

00:04:50.460 --> 00:04:52.459
Exactly, Father, did you hear that?

00:04:52.460 --> 00:04:53.579
She's a jinx.

00:04:53.580 --> 00:04:56.300
Misfortune follows her
wherever she goes, Father!

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:11.319
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:11.320 --> 00:05:15.159
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:18.679
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:21.640
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:22.520 --> 00:05:26.159
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:29.920
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:33.319
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:33.320 --> 00:05:37.360
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:46.639
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:46.640 --> 00:05:50.279
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:50.280 --> 00:05:53.999
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:57.639
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:57.640 --> 00:06:01.319
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:06:01.320 --> 00:06:03.239
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:06:03.240 --> 00:06:09.440
♪Good fortune♪